data.title: 1913) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Mrs. Elizabeth Ann Walker, of 101 Linden avenue, wife of the late Thomas Walker, died at the home of Mrs. George Walker, Summitville, N.Y., at 5:30 p.m., Sept. 9, 1913, at the age of 81 years, 5 months and 5 days.
